    "description": "<i>Craftimals: Build to the Sun</i> is the return of a classic! Originally an Xbox Live Indie Game fan favorite, this relaxing sandbox platformer combines simple block-stacking with adorable animal characters on a journey straight to the sky.<br><br>🧱 Use intuitive building mechanics to construct your own path<br><br>🐾 Team up in 2-player local co-op or go it alone<br><br>🌞 Reach checkpoints to unlock new powers, cute hats, and other surprises<br><br>🎨 Place blocks freely (no grids, no limits) and build in any direction<br><br>Whether you're chasing the sun, creating sky-high art, or just enjoying some stress-free platforming, <i>Craftimals</i> is a wholesome experience for all ages.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br>🧩 Easy-to-learn building with satisfying vertical progression<br><br>👯‍♂️ Local 2-player, split screen co-op<br><br>🎵 New soundtrack by Audionautix<br><br>🧢 Hats (so many hats)<br><br>🖌️ Creative freedom in a giant, open canvas<br><br>🏆 Steam achievements and leaderboards<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What's New (and What's Not)</h2><br>This is a faithful PC port of the 2012 original, now updated with keyboard/mouse support and some modern Steam perks.<br><br>If you're looking for a more advanced evolution of this idea, then check out our other game, <i>Doggo Dig Down</i>, which is the spiritual successor to <i>Craftimals</i>.",
